imdb.plot outline: An informative and exciting series, using treasure exhumed from the world's oceans to learn about the technologies and science of lost civilizations and periods of historical interest. The series showcases five dramatic stories set at sea, the clues to which are buried deep beneath the waves: ancient Egyptian boats, lost World War II planes, sunken cities and shipwreck treasure.
